OL,3,CUninsured driver bought policy minutes
OL,4,Cafter fatal crash
OL,6,FAn uninsured driver who bought a new
OL,7,Fpolicy within minutes of killing a
OL,8,Fmotorcyclist in an "act of self-
OL,9,Fpreservation" has been jailed.
OL,11,FCameron Ward, 30, was driving a Ford
OL,12,FFiesta when he crashed into Gregory
OL,13,FNewcombe's Harley-Davidson bike, on
OL,14,Fthe A684 near Bedale, North Yorkshire,
OL,15,Fon 10 July 2022.
OL,17,FMr Newcombe, 26, was thrown into the
OL,18,Fair, landing on the car's roof and
OL,19,Fthen rolling onto the ground nearby.
OL,20,FHe died at the scene.
