OL,6,FMinutes later, Ward called an
OL,7,Finsurance company and bought a one-day
OL,8,Fpolicy.
OL,10,FDet Ch Insp Jeremey Bartley, of North
OL,11,FYorkshire Police, said: "Despite being
OL,12,Funinsured, he attempted to cover up
OL,13,Fhis negligence by purchasing insurance
OL,14,Fjust minutes after the crash ` a clear
OL,15,Fact of self-preservation while a young
OL,16,Fman lay dying on the road due to his
OL,17,Factions.
