OL,6,F"Though the defendant had no intention
OL,7,Fof causing harm, his reckless
OL,8,Fbehaviour led to the devastating loss
OL,9,Fof a young life, robbing him of the
OL,10,Ffuture he could have shared with his
OL,11,Ffamily."
OL,13,FA witness confirmed Ward had pulled
OL,14,Fout onto the road in front of Mr
OL,15,FNewcombe's bike.
OL,17,FWard claimed bright sunlight had
OL,18,Fblinded him as he looked out but
OL,19,Finvestigators disproved the claim.
