OL,6,FWard was jailed for 10 months for
OL,7,Fcausing death by careless driving,
OL,8,Fdriving without insurance and
OL,9,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Mr Newcombe's family
OL,12,Fsaid: "There are no words to describe
OL,13,Fthe enormous void and loss that has
OL,14,Fbeen created.
OL,16,F"Greg was a lovely caring young man
OL,17,Fwho had everything to live for.
